Class GemInventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • items.GemInventory

  • public class GemInventory
extends java.lang.Object
    GemInventory is a collection of gems available to the player. It stores it in an ArrayList of GemInventory.Gem. It also ensures that there are at most 9 Gems.

    Changes: The class now properly renders, and provides better interaction between Gem and other classes.

    Total Time Spent: 1 hour(s).

    Version:
    2.0.0.0
    Author:
    Lev Raizman
